---
const corePrinciples = [
  { title: 'Systems over Isolated Tools', desc: 'Hệ thống quan trọng hơn công cụ rời rạc.' },
  { title: 'Data-driven Action', desc: 'Dữ liệu chỉ có giá trị khi nó tạo ra hành động.' },
  { title: 'Minimalist Professionalism', desc: 'Sự tối giản là đỉnh cao của sự phức tạp.' }
];
---

<section id="about-me" class="w-full min-h-screen flex items-center py-10 px-8 md:px-12 bg-background relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-12 gap-10 relative z-10 w-full">
    <!-- Left: Identity Meta -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-6 reveal">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-primary"></span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 border border-primary/40 rounded text-[9px] font-mono text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
          [ IDENTITY_LOG_V1.0 ]
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-foreground leading-[0.9] uppercase">
        Xây dựng <br />
        <span class="text-primary italic">Trật tự</span> từ <br />
        Dữ liệu.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed text-base font-medium border-l border-border pl-6">
        <p>
          Với nền tảng <span class="text-foreground font-bold">Applied Statistics</span>, tôi không chỉ code — tôi thiết kế các kiến trúc có khả năng <span class="text-foreground">Tự vận hành</span> và <span class="text-foreground">Tối ưu hóa</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
          Từ Dell Precision đến hệ thống Cluster, mục tiêu của tôi là kết nối các node rời rạc thành một bộ máy thống nhất.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-foreground/[0.04] border border-border/80 rounded-2xl glass-premium">
        <p class="text-xs italic leading-relaxed text-muted font-mono uppercase tracking-tight">
          "Intelligence is the ability to <span class="text-primary font-bold">Predict</span> and <span class="text-primary font-bold">Self-Adjust</span>."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Core Principles Grid -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center gap-3 reveal">
      <h3 class="text-[8px] font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-2 ml-2">System_Core_Directives</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {corePrinciples.map((p, i) => (
          <div class={`p-6 rounded-3xl border border-border/80 bg-card/30 glass-premium hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden ${i === 0 ? 'md:col-span-2' : ''}`}>
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">0{i+1}</span>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">{p.title}</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors">{p.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <!-- Operational Motto -->
      <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-foreground/[0.02] border border-border rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-lg">
          ◈
        </div>
        <p class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Designing the bridge between <span class="text-foreground font-bold">Mathematical Logic</span> and <span class="text-foreground font-bold">Operational Excellence</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .glass-premium {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
</style>
